msgstr "绑定所有出站连接到接口:"

#: htdocs/luci-static/resources/view/justclash/proxy.js:73
msgid "Bind Mihomo outbound connections to a specific network device by default. Leave empty to let the system choose the outgoing interface. Per-proxy and per-provider interface settings should override this value when set."
